title.rendered: Luxurious 4 BHK Apartment For Sale In Anand Niketan

content.rendered:
Coming up on the market is this stunning 4BHK apartment nestled in the most sought-after location of Anand Niketan. This plush home boasts 4 tidy & spacious bedrooms with adjoining bathrooms & spacious balconies, and a separate drawing dining room with grandeur interiors and furniture. a splendid modern kitchen, and separate car parking space. This home is located in the corner building thus it gets ample sunlight and ventilation. Anand Niketan is one of the most preferred areas for Expatriates, Diplomats, Beurocrats, Businessmen, and Industrialists. Anand Niketan is also in close proximity to Airport & Chanakyapuri which has an Embassy cluster, American and British schools, and luxury hotels like Taj & ITC Maurya.

♕4BHK For Sale

♕1st Floor

♕Corner Building

♕Big Hall

♕Separate Drawing Dining Room

♕Plush Interiors

♕WIde Road

♕Adjoining Park

Lalit Kaushik

Call On 98183-12077 For Site Visit

http://wa.me/919818312077

Follow @royalerealtorsindia on social media
Checkout Our Other Listings Here
ROYALE REALTORS INDIA

Royale Realtors India – Luxury Real Estate

19 DDA Market, Shanti Niketan, New Delhi, Delhi 110021
